[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ## confidence_score                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1.0                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ## thoughts                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The vulnerability exploitation was successful. The application uses insecure [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m direct object references where changing the `userid` in the serialized       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m cookie grants access to other users' data. User ID 1 contained a note titled [32m│[0m
